## Upgrade to Green deployment


ubuntu@ip-172-31-21-52:~/course3_projects/kubernetes_app_deployment_kustomize_helm_kudo/2b_helm/helm/advanced-deployments$ helm upgrade bluegreen --set "currentTarget.app=green" .
